Package: ADS8192
Title: ADS 8192 - Developing Scientific Applications (Course Materials)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jared", "Andrews", email = "jared.andrews@stjude.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Course materials and reference implementation for ADS 8192:
    Developing Scientific Applications. Demonstrates separation of concerns
    and layered architecture: PCA analysis functions for
    SummarizedExperiment objects, a Shiny interactive explorer, and a
    command-line interface via Rapp. Includes lectures, quizzes, and a
    grading rubric. Students build their own packages from simple
    raw project code following this model.
